<h1>Payment Successfully Initiated</h1>

<p>Dear <%= @client.name %>,</p>

<p>
  We are pleased to inform you that your payment for the task titled "<strong><%= @task.title %></strong>" has been successfully initiated and is currently pending approval.
</p>

<p><strong>Payment Summary:</strong></p>
<table style="width:100%; border-collapse: collapse;">
  <tr style="border-bottom: 1px solid #ddd;">
    <th style="text-align:left; padding: 8px;">Task:</th>
    <td style="padding: 8px;"><%= @task.title %></td>
  </tr>
  <tr style="border-bottom: 1px solid #ddd;">
    <th style="text-align:left; padding: 8px;">Amount:</th>
    <td style="padding: 8px;"><%= number_to_currency(@task.budget, unit: "ZMK ") %></td>
  </tr>
  <tr style="border-bottom: 1px solid #ddd;">
    <th style="text-align:left; padding: 8px;">Status:</th>
    <td style="padding: 8px;"><%= @payment.status.titleize %></td>
  </tr>
</table>

<p>
  You will receive a notification once the payment has been approved. Should you have any inquiries or require further assistance, please do not hesitate to contact our support team.
</p>

<p>Thank you for utilizing GigHive.</p>

<p>Sincerely,<br>The GigHive Team</p>